summary: This is an automatic reply email from Expedia's Law Enforcement Response Team acknowledging receipt of a law enforcement request regarding Maxwell. It indicates law enforcement was seeking information from Expedia, likely related to travel records or bookings.

events.title: Law Enforcement Request to Expedia Regarding Maxwell
events.description: An automatic reply email is sent from Expedia's Law Enforcement Response Team acknowledging receipt of a law enforcement request concerning Maxwell.

keyFacts: Law enforcement made a request to Expedia regarding Maxwell on or before February 7, 2020.
Expedia has a dedicated Law Enforcement Response Team to handle such requests.
The email is an automatic reply, indicating the request was received and a response would follow.
